## üéØ FAZA 6: Stack-Specific Configuration (15 minute)

### Obiectivul Fazei 6

ConfigureazƒÉ Storybook pentru func»õionarea optimƒÉ cu stack-ul specific Coquinate: React 19, Next 15 RSC, Tailwind v4 + OKLCH, »ôi monorepo cu pnpm.

### 6.1 React 19 + Next 15 RSC

- Storybook ruleazƒÉ **client-only** - extrage UI √Æn componente client
- Nu pune direct RSC pages √Æn Storybook
- FƒÉ wrapper components pentru RSC parts

### 6.2 Tailwind v4 + OKLCH

- Import `globals.css` √Æn preview.tsx ‚úÖ
- ScaneazƒÉ »ôi `.storybook/**/*` pentru clase:

```javascript
// tailwind.config.js
export default {
  content: [
    './packages/ui/src/**/*.{ts,tsx,mdx}',
    './packages/ui/.storybook/**/*.{ts,tsx,mdx}',
    './packages/ui/**/*.mdx', // Pentru Docs/MDX pages
  ],
  /* OKLCH tokens */
};
```

### 6.3 Monorepo cu pnpm

- `vite-tsconfig-paths` = zero drift pentru aliases
- `peerDependencies` = evitƒÉ React duplicates
- `sideEffects: false` = tree-shaking mai bun

### 6.4 Un Singur React √Æn Workspace

```json
// La root - package.json sau pnpm-workspace.yaml
{
  "pnpm": {
    "overrides": {
      "react": "^19.0.0",
      "react-dom": "^19.0.0"
    }
  }
}
```

