## üéØ FAZA 9: Troubleshooting »ôi Finalizare (10 minute)

### Obiectivul Fazei 9

RezolvƒÉ problemele comune »ôi finalizeazƒÉ setup-ul pentru utilizare √Æn produc»õie.

### 9.1 Troubleshooting Rapid

| ProblemƒÉ                             | Solu»õie                                                                                 |
| ------------------------------------ | --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| ClasƒÉ Tailwind nu apare              | VerificƒÉ globs √Æn `tailwind.config.js` (ai `src`, `.storybook`, `**/*.mdx` ‚úî)          |
| "Invalid hook call / douƒÉ React-uri" | `peerDependencies` + `pnpm overrides` (vezi mai sus)                                    |
| MSW nu intercepteazƒÉ                 | `initialize({ onUnhandledRequest: 'bypass' })` + `parameters.msw.handlers` pe URL exact |
| SVG ca componentƒÉ nu merge           | `vite-plugin-svgr` √Æn `viteFinal` ‚úî                                                    |

### 9.2 Quick Start (5 minute)

```bash
# 1. Setup cu Vite + toate extensiile
cd packages/ui
pnpm dlx storybook@latest init --builder=vite
pnpm add -D @storybook/addon-themes msw msw-storybook-addon vite-tsconfig-paths @storybook/test vite-plugin-svgr

# 2. Copy config-urile de mai sus
# main.ts + preview.tsx + tsconfig.json + package.json

# 3. Start
pnpm storybook

# 4. See it
# http://localhost:6006
```

