### Core Setup

- ‚úÖ **Zero drift**: `vite-tsconfig-paths` pentru aliases
- ‚úÖ **React 19 ready**: `reactDocgen` + `peerDependencies`
- ‚úÖ **MSW realistic**: `onUnhandledRequest: 'bypass'`
- ‚úÖ **Providers globali**: Theme + i18n √Æn decorators
- ‚úÖ **SVG support**: `vite-plugin-svgr`
- ‚úÖ **Test interactions**: `@storybook/test` + `jest-dom`

### Production Optimizations

- ‚úÖ **Clean publishes**: `"files": ["dist"]`
- ‚úÖ **Tree-shaking**: `sideEffects: false` + `treeshake: true`
- ‚úÖ **Minified builds**: conditional minify √Æn tsup
- ‚úÖ **Sourcemaps**: pentru debugging √Æn production
- ‚úÖ **A11y checks**: `@storybook/addon-a11y` automat

### Quality & Scaling

- ‚úÖ **Tailwind coverage**: Include `.storybook/**/*` + `**/*.mdx`
- ‚úÖ **Assets support**: `staticDirs` pentru imagini
- ‚úÖ **CI-ready tests**: `test:sb` cu proper config-dir
- ‚úÖ **Design tokens**: MDX page pentru AI + oameni

