### ‚úÖ BOOST #1: Generator OBLIGATORIU

- **Alias rapid**: `pnpm -F @coquinate/ui g` ‚Üí Component + Story + Test √Æn <30s
- **Modern Hearth built-in**: Template-urile includ OKLCH + glass + CVA + focus states
